  "description": "This quiz tests a developer's proficiency with JavaScript's native Date API, focusing on date manipulation, formatting, and localization without relying on third-party libraries. It operates at an intermediate to advanced difficulty level, using a playful and encouraging tone to demystify the API's notoriously quirky design. The material is crafted to help developers build confidence in core language features.",
